divs: sighting detailsi was exercising in my spa at 1:15 on a wed. afternoon, 9\19\2012 when i noticed an object in the sky , it was north traveling in a straight line going northeast,ther were alot of larger clouds in the sky ,but alot of blue sky also, at first the object that appeared frisbee shaped with a dome was black ,then silverish , maybe when the sun reflected,i watched it for appr. 15-20 seconds when it went behind a fairly large cloud and counted the seconds i thought it would take to get across the cloud, well it never came out the other side, there was no vapor trail or any sign of propulsion and i watched the sky for another half hour and it never came to my view again.
Summary: sitting in spa on back porch at 1:15pm, i noticed a frisbee shape with a dome, it was moving from north to northeast.
